CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 11, 1964, pg. 24, reads: "Repeat Champions - Members of the Baptist Temple basketball team of Homewood recently became champions of the Homewood- Brushton YMCA Basketball League for the third year in a row. Baptist Temple defeated Bethesda Church in finals.  Team members are (left to right) Petey Davis, Joe Lewis, coach; Billy Ryan, Varnell Lewis, Leon Fuler, Kenny Kemp, Curtis Ezell and the Rev. J.A. Williams, the pastor of Baptist Temple. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Baptist Temple basketball team, from left: Petey Davis, Joe Lewis, coach; Billy Ryan, Varnell Lewis, Leon Fuler, Kenny Kemp, Curtis Ezell and Rev. J.A. Williams, posed with trophy for Homewood-Brushton YMCA basketball league championship
